node.title: BBL live: Sixers and Stars get new Big Bash season underway
node.alt: The Big Bash League trophy sits on the deck of a boat in front of a BBL sign in Hobart.
node.description: The new Big Bash season is underway, with the Sydney Sixers and Melbourne Stars launching the new campaign. Get all the live scores and stats in our ScoreCentre.
